title: Best of CCK: Hells Bells
description:
KFC and Carrabis reminisce about the time Chrissy Teigen and Dave went at each other over Twitter, the Milton days, the original Barstoo Radio of an MMA channel, the Comedy Central Super Bowl, the Combine and Grudgement Day. Also TikTok drama, first baseball memories and how to change ROugh N Rowdy.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
